{"tid":2029361,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，早排有個 post 就講緊 Minecraft BTE 1:1 世界計劃","createTime":"2020-05-22T07:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T06:50:25.000Z","uid":254558,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0eea609382b525a26c612ca738efaf63ad99172c","tid":2029361,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早排有個 post 就講緊 Minecraft BTE 1:1 世界計劃<br />\n你哋咪話好想要server嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Build</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">The</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">Earth</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">Official</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Team HK-MU</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同大家介紹下先，Build The Earth係一個希望係Minecraft用1:1方式起曬全世界嘅project，而我哋就係BTE官方嘅香港澳門建築團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，主要目標就梗係以1:1最真實嘅比例同方式起曬成個香港同澳門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋喺呢一兩個月嘅假期嗰時已經起咗好多唔同嘅建築，例如公屋呀、貨櫃碼頭呀<br />\n(連機場都有條痴線佬差唔多起曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skt3WnE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkt3WnE.png&h=a2a3ab65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApEZuHH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApEZuHH.png&h=f3e2a51e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LJ8b5f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLJ8b5f3.png&h=74c1a758&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdNwkPq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdNwkPq.png&h=735a3333&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WhPRZJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WhPRZJ.png&h=ed7ab271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問題就黎啦，香港地方咁大，得幾丁友我哋一定起唔曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋需要你哋既幫手</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n無論你起嘢勁唔勁，可以付出既時間得幾多，甚至唔玩Minecraft但係想係其他方面幫我哋既，我哋都隨時歡迎你加入我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果各位巴絲有興趣嘅話，歡迎follow番我哋IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋加入番BTE官方同我哋條Team嘅Discord群組(依家已經有200幾條友㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\nTeam HK-MU IG: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/btehkmu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbtehkmu&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fe229831\" target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/btehkmu</a><br />\nTeam HK-MU DC: <a href=\"http://discord.gg/E7BCNgj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FE7BCNgj&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c616f110\" target=\"_blank\">discord.gg/E7BCNgj</a><br />\nBTE Official: <a href=\"http://discord.gg/tanUx4b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FtanUx4b&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f528b28c\" target=\"_blank\">discord.gg/tanUx4b</a><br />\n係入咗我哋群組之後，更加會有入埋我哋Minecraft server嘅教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa330b75ba0e556c01a96dcfef803969a32a225","tid":2029361,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c